---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DownloadButtons from '@/components/DownloadButtons.astro';
import { withBase } from '@/lib/paths';
---

<BaseLayout title="Huaxia Civic Uprising, Transformation, and Jurisprudence of Normalization" description="English overview of the Chinese academic book project.">
  <section class="bg-navy-950 text-ivory">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-gold-pale/82">English Overview</p>
      <h1 class="mt-5 font-serif text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight sm:text-5xl">Huaxia Civic Uprising, Transformation, and Jurisprudence of Normalization</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-ivory/76">This page provides an English-facing entry point for a Chinese academic book organized around the concepts of inner disposition, name-reality analysis, collective environment, jurisprudence, and normalization.</p>
      <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a class="border border-gold-muted/50 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-gold-pale transition hover:bg-gold-muted hover:text-navy-950" href={withBase('/book/preface/')}>Read Chinese Text</a>
        <DownloadButtons compact />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="paper-texture bg-ivory text-ink">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <article class="academic-prose prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2>Editorial Note</h2>
        <p>The full book is currently presented in Chinese. Strong historical and political claims are presented as the author’s thesis and interpretive framework, not as neutral factual assertions by the website.</p>
        <h2>Core Concepts</h2>
        <p><strong>心境</strong> concerns inner disposition and judgment. <strong>名实</strong> concerns the relation between names, concepts, and realities. <strong>群境</strong> concerns collective life and institutional environment. These concepts lead into the author’s discussion of jurisprudence and normalization.</p>
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Publication, translation, and editorial contact: <a href="mailto:yc114de@gmail.com">yc114de@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
